title: "DTMC-GA Modularization Reproducibility Artifact"
version: "0.3.4-phase3C-ci-ready"
message: "Please cite the associated manuscript. This Phase 3C artifact contains local executable benchmark-suite evidence, retained raw results, Dockerfile improvements, and GitHub Actions CI verification workflow. A public repository URL and Zenodo DOI remain pending and must be inserted after archival and before final journal submission."
